{"tid":2438401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"規劃將主教山打造微型郊野公園","createTime":"2021-03-08T12:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T13:32:39.000Z","uid":285248,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"85353563b8d10fd07895658c962131ff934b182a","tid":2438401,"uid":285248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:53:59.000Z","msg":"咩料，仲話要拆上蓋。唔喺知佢係文物，所以弱化要保護，而喺知佢弱化，所以要拆⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//逾百年歷史的主教山配水庫險遭拆毀惹來廣泛關注，古物古蹟辦事處早前向古物諮詢委員會就上述配水庫建議評級，並建議列為一級歷史建築，該會將於周四開會討論。規劃署前署長凌嘉勤指，配水庫的上蓋可能已經弱化，擔心未來未必可以承受大量市民前往參觀，認爲可拆除部分上蓋，減低危險性。同時他建議政府，應盡量保留其配水庫自然狀態，並考慮規劃整個主教山，及打造成「鬧市中的微型郊野公園」。//<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AjwZFkf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAjwZFkf.jpg&h=2c71325e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%BB%E6%95%99%E5%B1%B1%E9%85%8D%E6%B0%B4%E5%BA%AB%E4%B8%8A%E8%93%8B%E5%BC%B1%E5%8C%96-%E8%A6%8F%E5%8A%83%E7%BD%B2%E5%89%8D%E7%BD%B2%E9%95%B7%E7%B1%B2%E6%89%93%E9%80%A0%E5%BE%AE%E5%9E%8B%E9%83%8A%E9%87%8E%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92-103014291.html?ncid=facebook_hkfacebook_a19b6y3mefk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E9%2585%258D%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%25BA%25AB%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%2593%258B%25E5%25BC%25B1%25E5%258C%2596-%25E8%25A6%258F%25E5%258A%2583%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E9%2595%25B7%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%2580%25A0%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E5%259E%258B%25E9%2583%258A%25E9%2587%258E%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%2592-103014291.html%3Fncid%3Dfacebook_hkfacebook_a19b6y3mefk&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv0wFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=ea81e451\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%BB%E6%95%99%E5%B1%B1%E9%85%8D%E6%B0%B4%E5%BA%AB%E4%B8%8A%E8%93%8B%E5%BC%B1%E5%8C%96-%E8%A6%8F%E5%8A%83%E7%BD%B2%E5%89%8D%E7%BD%B2%E9%95%B7%E7%B1%B2%E6%89%93%E9%80%A0%E5%BE%AE%E5%9E%8B%E9%83%8A%E9%87%8E%E5%85%